snippet: Pint-sized point guard Isaiah Thomas scored 23 points in three quarters, and five other players finished in double figures as the Boston Celtics kept John Wall in check and beat the Washington Wizards 116-91 on Monday night....
lead_paragraph: Pint-sized point guard Isaiah Thomas scored 23 points in three quarters, and five other players finished in double figures as the Boston Celtics kept John Wall in check and beat the Washington Wizards 116-91 on Monday night.

headline.main: Thomas Lights Up Wizards as Celtics Win 3rd Straight, 116-91
headline.print_headline: Thomas Lights Up Wizards as Celtics Win 3rd Straight, 116-91
